Liverpool have officially announced the signing of Fabio Carvalho and the player has spoken of his delight of joining the Reds. “It’s just an amazing feeling to be here at one of the biggest clubs in the world, if not the biggest. So, I’m just happy to be here and I can’t wait to get started,” Carvalho told Liverpoolfc.com. “Once you hear that Liverpool are interested, there’s only one thought in your mind, which is to join them and try to be in and around the team. Hopefully I can achieve big things. “I spoke with everyone, and the manager, and it just felt so natural. When things become natural it’s just so much easier to make a decision.”